Package com.example.flexiMed.model

Class AmbulanceEntity

java.lang.Object
com.example.flexiMed.model.AmbulanceEntity
@Entity public class AmbulanceEntity extends Object
Entity representing an ambulance in the system. This class includes data such as the ambulance's plate number, driver details, location, availability status, driver reference, and timestamps.
